     <article class="post-76217 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-arts category-science-technology tag-diversity tag-engineering tag-entertainment"> 
      <a class="category-link arts" href="/category/arts/" title="View all stories in Arts">Arts</a>
